5:
Open the gun ports! Charge up the
dracocannons!
26:
Direct hit on all counts... I think? But
now they're totally firing back! NOT
COOL!
30:
Shields are holding. Damage is
minimal. We can still keep going.
36:
We're all countin' on ya, Yu-yu!
Same for you, princies!
41:
We've got bigger
problems—enemies on our tail!
They're dragon-types... and they're
growing in number!
45:
Let the old guys handle anti-air
combat! Shift into reverse and bring
'er in low. We're deploying the
ground troops!
51:
Our inertial control device has heard
your order, Cap'n. His response is,
and I'm quoting here, "Are you trying
to kill me, or what?!"
60:
Tell him you'll throw in a "special"
reward later. That ought to motivate
him.
66:
Alk! Stella! Don't you worry! Your
crew is on the way!
86:
Hahaha! You've got some serious
firepower, Bulleta! Just the kinda gal
to get my servos singing! Care to
make a wager on who can pop
more pests?
90:
Sure, but since there's no ammo bill
for me to worry about, your chances
aren't looking too good, tin man.
96:
Hey! What about ME? Can I join?
Please? Come on! Hey! Why are you
ignoring me?!
101: Tohru, old pal, how would you li—
106:
Ground troops coming out. I'll
provide cover.
120:
It seems to be time for another
dragon hunt... Time for you to shine,
Murakumo!
124:
Understood! By my blade shall
history be carved!
128:
Our enemy may be the Origin
Dragon itself... But that does not
mean our resolve will falter!
131: Fight on, Champions of the Stars!
135:
All of our power—our prayers—will
be entrusted to you, Inaho!
139: Go, go, go! Inaho can do it!
144:
That I can! You may count on me to
see this done!
150:
To five elements—six companions
converge—countless paths laid
bare. 
Unto one existence, three thousand
realms unite!
165:
Behold the golden power of Nine
Tails!
174: None of us are in this alone...
178:
This doesn't have to be the end—for
either of us!
182:
You don't understand... The dragon
can't be defeated. It is the very
source of causality—of fate itself!
185:
But, you're right... Things cannot end
the way they are now!
189:
Ayumu Nagihara! Your very
existence hinders my plans!
197:
I was wrong. The Overlords were
never my enemy. Neither was the
Goddess of the Stars, nor the
Champions...
211:
I won't allow anyone else to
interfere... 
These are our final moments!
215: This is where it all ends, Alk!
219:
No! We've only just begun! We still
have a future ahead of us!
223:
We'll prove that to you...
No matter what it takes.
